286
00:19:25,067 --> 00:19:26,735
-It's not every day a
champion plays online.

287
00:19:29,371 --> 00:19:30,005
BOY: Oh.

288
00:19:30,039 --> 00:19:31,073
BOY: Is this it?

289
00:19:31,073 --> 00:19:32,408
BOY: Wow.

290
00:19:32,441 --> 00:19:34,209
-What a showdown.

