00:19:53,095 --> 00:19:55,164
-Don't forget they're
playing an even game.

300
00:19:55,197 --> 00:19:57,366
If white's playing this
well with no handicap--

301
00:19:57,366 --> 00:19:58,467
-Whoa!

302
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:00,202
They've both got three
hours of playing time.

303
00:20:00,235 --> 00:20:01,503
AKIRA (VOICEOVER): Three hours?

304
00:20:01,503 --> 00:20:03,205
This is no ordinary opponent.

305
00:20:03,238 --> 00:20:05,174
Who's he playing, anyway?

306
00:20:05,207 --> 00:20:08,711
-Um. Let's see.

