00:20:16,118 --> 00:20:17,086
-No idea.

312
00:20:29,565 --> 00:20:31,433
-Never heard of
him, but he's got

313
00:20:31,467 --> 00:20:33,135
to be a pro to play like this.

314
00:20:33,168 --> 00:20:34,436
-You'd think so.

315
00:20:34,470 --> 00:20:36,105
-Hm.

316
00:20:36,138 --> 00:20:37,339
AKIRA (VOICEOVER): It can't be!

317
00:20:42,111 --> 00:20:43,445
It's Sai!

318
00:20:43,479 --> 00:20:44,613
He's back in the game!

319
00:20:48,550 --> 00:20:51,754
